{
  "stem": "1641.4",
  "chunk_idx": 15,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 111,
      "text": "And the next day, the next day some people managed to get one barrel of hot coffee-- I mean hot water, which I got one cup of it.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 112,
      "text": "And the next day again, the next night went past standing outside.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 113,
      "text": "We still couldn't get to the shower room.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 114,
      "text": "And then came the third morning.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 115,
      "text": "And I had a brilliant idea.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 116,
      "text": "I was very sick.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 117,
      "text": "I had temperature.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 118,
      "text": "But I had a brilliant idea.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 119,
      "text": "I met the other doctor and the dentist from Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 120,
      "text": "And we were-- we realized we are very far back from the shower place.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 121,
      "text": "But we realized if we don't get through before nightfall, before the night comes-- because nighttime it's much colder than the daytime-- then we shall freeze to death the next night.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 122,
      "text": "Because we were very, very weak.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 123,
      "text": "So we thought, we have to make an effort to get to the shower.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 124,
      "text": "And the thing to do is to put on our Auschwitz band-- arm bands, and try to look as official as possible.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 125,
      "text": "And-- and we started to shout in the best [GERMAN] like the Berlin accent.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 126,
      "text": "[GERMAN], you know, make room.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 127,
      "text": "And, you know, doctor coming.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 128,
      "text": "[GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 129,
      "text": "Make room for the interpreter.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 130,
      "text": "And people were already half unconscious anyhow, the ones who were not dead yet.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 131,
      "text": "And so we could step over dead bodies and half-dead people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 132,
      "text": "And [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 133,
      "text": "You know, and we just gently pushed them aside.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 134,
      "text": "And we jumped the queue.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 135,
      "text": "We jumped the queue so to say, because we were very, very much back.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 136,
      "text": "We knew that we are dying if we don't get forward.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 137,
      "text": "Well--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
